==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Patriotic
<hw>Pa`tri*ot"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>patriotique</ets>, Gr. <grk>patriwtiko`s</grk> belonging to a
fellow-countryman.]</ety> <def>Inspired by patriotism; actuated by love
of one's country; zealously and unselfishly devoted to the service of
one's country; <as>as, a <ex>patriotic</ex> statesman,
vigilance</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Patriotical</ent>⟦br⟧
